{"tid":970555,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"畢馬威統計 尼馬最值錢 垃圾C朗不入10大","createTime":"2019-01-06T02:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T06:28:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e3e1b68b030c9d03ed808994e6e4d222fab231","tid":970555,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ew77jXDyOYNVIOodbIO3mOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=683b06df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】根據世界4大會計師事務所畢馬威統計，尼馬為世界上最值錢足球員，但基斯坦奴朗拿度卻不入前10位。<br />\n<br />\n在畢馬威的統計，以位置、年齡、國籍、表現、商業市場等方面，去計算世界各地足球員的價值。全球最高轉會費紀錄保持者尼馬（Neymar）仍然是最有價值球員，總值2.065億鎊，次席為尼馬的巴黎聖日耳門前線拍檔基利安麥巴比，值1.938億鎊，而巴塞隆拿前鋒美斯就以1.832億鎊排第3位。<br />\n<br />\n第4至7位都是英超球員，先後是利物浦前鋒穆罕默德沙拿（1.516億鎊）、熱刺射手哈利卡尼（1.361億鎊）、車路士翼鋒夏薩特（1.335億鎊）、曼城中場奇雲迪布尼（1.166億鎊）。至於最近重生的曼聯中場保羅普巴，就以1.075億鎊排第9位。<br />\n<br />\n今季從皇家馬德里加盟祖雲達斯的球王基斯坦奴朗拿度，由於在2月就滿34歲，年紀較大，因此價值只得9650鎊，排在10大之外。"},{"pid":"bc496721e214f16361efffa6a6146602ffa55429","tid":970555,"uid":204475,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"9650鎊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪漏咗個萬字呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a937155e6109a85e2fdfdb104a8ba6ee457ab7f","tid":970555,"uid":8733,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"bc496721e214f16361efffa6a6146602ffa55429","tid":970555,"uid":204475,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"9650鎊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=